Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.95,0:00:13.32,Default,Kugisaki,0,0,0,,Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.96,0:00:16.84,Default,Yuji,0,0,0,,You've done it now, Kugisaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.84,0:00:19.28,Default,Yuji,0,0,0,,This was Gojo{*}{*-sensei}'s, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.64,0:00:30.32,Default,Kugisaki,0,0,0,,Between Ijichi{**-san}, who left us in charge of this freshly cleaned shirt,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.86,0:00:32.93,Default,Kugisaki,0,0,0,,and me, who spilled coffee on it...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.33,0:00:34.51,Default,Kugisaki,0,0,0,,Who's more at fault?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.51,0:00:35.39,Default,Both,0,0,0,,You.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.01,0:00:39.04,Default,Yuji,0,0,0,,You pat it down, pat it down.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.04,0:00:40.27,Default,Kugisaki,0,0,0,,I'm working on it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.24,0:00:51.20,Default,Yuji,0,0,0,,It kind of looks like a marimekko.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.20,0:00:52.94,Default,Fushiguro,0,0,0,,Don't take apparel so lightly.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.94,0:00:55.52,Default,Kugisaki,0,0,0,,Eh, I'm sure it's a cheap shirt, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.52,0:00:58.11,Default,Kugisaki,0,0,0,,Fushiguro, look up the brand on the tag.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.42,0:01:09.78,Default,Yuji,0,0,0,,A-After tax?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.78,0:01:11.07,Default,Fushiguro,0,0,0,,Before tax.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.07,0:01:12.56,Default,Fushiguro,0,0,0,,Is that even important?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.08,0:01:15.46,Default,Kugisaki,0,0,0,,We have no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.46,0:01:17.56,Default,Kugisaki,0,0,0,,I'll put in 90,000.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.56,0:01:19.24,Default,Kugisaki,0,0,0,,You can each put in 80,000.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.24,0:01:20.20,Default,Yuji,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.20,0:01:21.38,Default,Gojo,0,0,0,,Morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.38,0:01:23.97,Default,Gojo,0,0,0,,Ijichi said you guys had my shirt?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.44,0:01:27.39,Default,Gojo,0,0,0,,What's the matter, Megumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.39,0:01:28.81,Default,Fushiguro,0,0,0,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.08,0:01:58.79,Default,Yuji,0,0,0,,Kugisaki...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.24,0:02:10.56,Default,Yuji,0,0,0,,I-I can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.81,0:02:27.08,Default,Mahito,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm thrilled!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.39,0:02:29.41,Default,Mahito,0,0,0,,{\i1}By my own talent!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.41,0:02:32.62,Default,Mahito,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ah, I really am...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.62,0:02:34.53,Default,Mahito,0,0,0,,{\i1}I truly am...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.88,0:02:36.88,Default,Mahito,0,0,0,,{\i1}a curse!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.00,0:02:41.35,Default,Mahito,0,0,0,,Black Flash!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.58,0:02:49.28,Default,Mahito,0,0,0,,I bet you just thought
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.28,0:02:51.56,Default,Mahito,0,0,0,,this would be some pest extermination,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.56,0:02:54.74,Default,Mahito,0,0,0,,or like defeating evil spirits in a legend,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.08,0:03:00.55,Default,Mahito,0,0,0,,or something like that when you came here, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.03,0:03:04.21,Default,Mahito,0,0,0,,You're naïve! You damn brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.21,0:03:07.08,Default,Mahito,0,0,0,,This is war!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.08,0:03:10.51,Default,Mahito,0,0,0,,It's not some fight to correct a mistake!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.51,0:03:13.30,Default,Mahito,0,0,0,,It's a clash of what we believe is right!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.30,0:03:17.54,Default,Mahito,0,0,0,,Of our own flimsy ideas of justice!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.10,0:03:25.76,Default,Mahito,0,0,0,,You are me, Itadori Yuji.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.08,0:03:33.81,Default,Mahito,0,0,0,,Just as I kill people without a second thought,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.40,0:03:38.80,Default,Mahito,0,0,0,,you save people without a second thought!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.80,0:03:40.65,Default,Mahito,0,0,0,,It's our instincts
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.65,0:03:44.08,Default,Mahito,0,0,0,,versus the dignity gained by human reasoning!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.08,0:03:50.20,Default,Mahito,0,0,0,,This is a war to determine which of those will be left standing a century from now!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.29,0:03:55.16,Default,Mahito,0,0,0,,If you haven't even realized that yet,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.16,0:03:57.58,Default,Mahito,0,0,0,,how are you supposed to beat me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.07,0:04:05.59,Default,Mahito,0,0,0,,Hey, Itadori Yuji.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.33,0:04:09.19,Default,Mahito,0,0,0,,Have you counted how many curses you've killed?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.60,0:04:13.33,Default,Mahito,0,0,0,,I bet not.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.33,0:04:14.72,Default,Mahito,0,0,0,,Me, neither!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.08,0:04:19.23,Default,Mahito,0,0,0,,I really couldn't care less about the number of humans I've killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.53,0:04:24.87,Default,Mahito,0,0,0,,Eventually, I'll forget all about you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.62,0:04:37.47,Default,Todo,0,0,0,,The bells of the Gion monastery in India
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.20,0:04:41.48,Default,Todo,0,0,0,,echo with the warning that all things are impermanent.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.63,0:04:45.96,Default,Todo,0,0,0,,The blossoms of the sala trees teach us through their hues
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.20,0:04:51.16,Default,Todo,0,0,0,,that what flourishes must fade.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.56,0:04:54.06,Default,Todo,0,0,0,,However!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.87,0:05:00.94,Default,Todo,0,0,0,,We are the exception!
Comment: 0,0:05:05.95,0:05:05.99,Default,chptr,0,0,0,,{Opening}
Comment: 0,0:06:35.96,0:06:36.00,Default,chptr,0,0,0,,{Part A}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.20,0:06:38.81,Default,Arata,0,0,0,,{\an8}These people...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.89,0:06:41.68,Default,Arata,0,0,0,,{\an8}are alive, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.48,0:06:52.39,Default,Todo,0,0,0,,It looks like Geto Suguru has already left with the Prison Realm.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.39,0:06:53.76,Default,Arata,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.64,0:06:56.22,Default,Todo,0,0,0,,Let's switch gears.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.72,0:06:59.76,Default,Todo,0,0,0,,Our goal has changed from fighting to reclaim Gojo Satoru
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.76,0:07:05.12,Default,Todo,0,0,0,,to fighting to save our allies and shave away as much of the enemy forces as possible,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.12,0:07:08.62,Default,Todo,0,0,0,,starting right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.24,0:07:11.53,Default,Todo,0,0,0,,Let's hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.53,0:07:14.42,Default,Todo,0,0,0,,My brother should already be nearby.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.44,0:07:17.46,Default,Arata,0,0,0,,{\i1}He has a brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.46,0:07:19.91,Default,Arata,0,0,0,,{\i1}I could have sworn he was an only child.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.01,0:07:26.02,Default,Mahito,0,0,0,,{\i1}What just happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.55,0:07:28.26,Default,Mahito,0,0,0,,{\i1}A face with a scar!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.26,0:07:30.66,Default,Mahito,0,0,0,,{\i1}Plus the way he switched places just now!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.66,0:07:33.00,Default,Mahito,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is he the sorcerer who drove Hanami into a corner?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.00,0:07:34.21,Default,Arata,0,0,0,,Todo{**-san}!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.21,0:07:36.57,Default,Arata,0,0,0,,I finished treating that girl over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.57,0:07:38.85,Default,Arata,0,0,0,,She's probably dead, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.85,0:07:41.38,Default,Arata,0,0,0,,So please don't blame me later!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.38,0:07:43.02,Default,Todo,0,0,0,,Enough prattle.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.02,0:07:44.51,Default,Todo,0,0,0,,See to my brother, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.51,0:07:46.44,Default,Todo,0,0,0,,Wake up, Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.44,0:07:49.01,Default,Todo,0,0,0,,Our battle has just begun!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.01,0:07:50.28,Default,Arata,0,0,0,,{\i1}Talk about ominous lines!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.20,0:07:54.97,Default,Yuji,0,0,0,,Todo...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.92,0:07:58.50,Default,Yuji,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.99,0:08:00.29,Default,Yuji,0,0,0,,can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.71,0:08:04.29,Default,Yuji,0,0,0,,fight anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.55,0:08:08.12,Default,Yuji,0,0,0,,It wasn't just Kugisaki...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.12,0:08:09.60,Default,Yuji,0,0,0,,Nanamin died, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.16,0:08:15.16,Default,Yuji,0,0,0,,Sukuna... killed so many.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.16,0:08:19.51,Default,Yuji,0,0,0,,So I have to save...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.51,0:08:22.27,Default,Yuji,0,0,0,,that many more people...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.35,0:08:25.47,Default,Yuji,0,0,0,,But I couldn't!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.47,0:08:27.96,Default,Yuji,0,0,0,,I'm just a murderer!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.36,0:08:33.36,Default,Yuji,0,0,0,,What I thought was my conviction
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.18,0:08:37.36,Default,Yuji,0,0,0,,was just an excuse I made for myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.86,0:08:45.54,Default,Yuji,0,0,0,,I can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.02,0:08:49.44,Default,Yuji,0,0,0,,forgive myself anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.38,0:08:54.20,Default,Mahito,0,0,0,,Speak up! I can't hear you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.11,0:09:12.36,Default,Mahito,0,0,0,,{\i1}Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.36,0:09:15.16,Default,Mahito,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even when you know about it, it's still this disorienting?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.88,0:09:17.55,Default,Todo,0,0,0,,Brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.55,0:09:21.41,Default,Todo,0,0,0,,A man as great as you shouldn't let yourself grow so small.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.74,0:09:24.15,Default,Todo,0,0,0,,We are jujutsu sorcerers.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.55,0:09:25.67,Default,Todo,0,0,0,,Me,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.67,0:09:27.17,Default,Todo,0,0,0,,you,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.17,0:09:28.55,Default,Todo,0,0,0,,Kugisaki,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.55,0:09:30.15,Default,Todo,0,0,0,,Mr. Nanami,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.54,0:09:35.19,Default,Todo,0,0,0,,and all of our allies are jujutsu sorcerers!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.04,0:09:38.33,Default,Todo,0,0,0,,So long as we continue to live,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.33,0:09:40.44,Default,Todo,0,0,0,,our dead comrades
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.44,0:09:43.68,Default,Todo,0,0,0,,have not truly been defeated!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.20,0:09:47.07,Default,Todo,0,0,0,,This is not a matter of sins and punishments.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.40,0:09:50.69,Default,Todo,0,0,0,,The moment we chose to live as jujutsu sorcerers,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.69,0:09:56.20,Default,Todo,0,0,0,,our lives were no longer bound by such karma.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.52,0:10:00.72,Default,Todo,0,0,0,,Attempting to find meaning in the deaths of the fallen
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.72,0:10:03.96,Default,Todo,0,0,0,,can, at times, defile the memories of those we've lost!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.71,0:10:05.96,Default,Todo,0,0,0,,But even so!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.94,0:10:10.72,Default,Todo,0,0,0,,What have they entrusted you with?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.43,0:10:17.60,Default,Todo,0,0,0,,There's no need to find your answer to that now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.86,0:10:20.25,Default,Todo,0,0,0,,But until you do,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.25,0:10:22.47,Default,Todo,0,0,0,,you cannot stop moving forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.01,0:10:26.36,Default,Todo,0,0,0,,That is the one punishment imposed
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.36,0:10:28.37,Default,Todo,0,0,0,,on those who live as jujutsu sorcerers.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.37,0:10:34.85,Default,Todo,0,0,0,,{\i1}There's no need to tell my brother about {\i0}that{\i1} right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.95,0:10:45.37,Default,Arata,0,0,0,,I've applied my technique to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.37,0:10:47.42,Default,Arata,0,0,0,,Now, listen up, Itadori{**-kun}.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.86,0:10:51.80,Default,Arata,0,0,0,,The wounds you have suffered so far will no longer worsen.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.21,0:10:53.70,Default,Arata,0,0,0,,They are {i}not{/i} healed,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.70,0:10:56.56,Default,Arata,0,0,0,,but you'll stop losing blood, and it should take the edge off the pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.56,0:10:59.00,Default,Arata,0,0,0,,But that only applies to your {\i1}current{\i0} wounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.65,0:11:02.41,Default,Arata,0,0,0,,If you take another attack, you'll be further wounded,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.41,0:11:06.09,Default,Arata,0,0,0,,and my technique won't apply to those.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.09,0:11:09.06,Default,Arata,0,0,0,,{\i1}Todo{**-san}'s little brother doesn't resemble him at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.64,0:11:12.64,Default,Arata,0,0,0,,I gave the girl over there the same treatment.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.37,0:11:16.54,Default,Arata,0,0,0,,She didn't have a pulse and wasn't breathing,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.54,0:11:18.30,Default,Arata,0,0,0,,but it hadn't been very long.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.30,0:11:20.42,Default,Arata,0,0,0,,The chance that she survives isn't zero.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.18,0:11:24.15,Default,Arata,0,0,0,,I'm taking her with me and getting out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.52,0:11:26.41,Default,Arata,0,0,0,,I'm just saying the chance isn't zero!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.41,0:11:28.61,Default,Arata,0,0,0,,Please don't get your hopes up too high!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.56,0:11:31.54,Default,Yuji,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.79,0:11:33.81,Default,Yuji,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.41,0:11:37.92,Default,Mahito,0,0,0,,Are you finished talking, topknot gorilla?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.30,0:12:28.81,Default,Todo,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.81,0:12:31.06,Default,Todo,0,0,0,,You won't touch me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.84,0:12:33.67,Default,Mahito,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's skilled.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.67,0:12:38.14,Default,Mahito,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's parrying me while also keeping distance from the nearly finished Itadori.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.50,0:12:41.35,Default,Mahito,0,0,0,,That's not all I've got.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.82,0:12:45.34,Default,Mahito,0,0,0,,{\i1}He dodged it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.34,0:12:47.44,Default,Mahito,0,0,0,,{\i1}Bring on the switch!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.44,0:12:48.92,Default,Mahito,0,0,0,,{\i1}This time, I'll adapt!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.92,0:12:50.62,Default,Mahito,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll hit him for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.29,0:12:54.08,Default,Mahito,0,0,0,,{\i1}I want to land that thing once more!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.44,0:12:57.33,Default,Mahito,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can feel myself close to reaching it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.68,0:13:00.95,Default,Mahito,0,0,0,,{\i1}The true essence of my soul!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.00,0:13:07.15,Default,Yuji,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm sorry, Nanamin.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.12,0:13:09.86,Default,Yuji,0,0,0,,{\i1}I was trying to take the easy way out.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.65,0:13:14.60,Default,Yuji,0,0,0,,{\i1}I even used my sins as an excuse to run away.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.95,0:13:19.80,Default,Nanami,0,0,0,,Please take it from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.77,0:13:22.57,Default,Yuji,0,0,0,,Black Flash!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.50,0:13:37.51,Default,Yuji,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll make sure I take on your share of suffering, too, Nanamin.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.41,0:13:46.38,Default,Mahito,0,0,0,,Tsk! Half-dead boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.49,0:13:57.10,Default,Todo,0,0,0,,Welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.60,0:13:58.24,Default,Yuji,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Comment: 0,0:14:00.03,0:14:00.07,Default,chptr,0,0,0,,{Part B}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.51,0:14:10.12,Default,Mechamaru,0,0,0,,{\i1}Matters should be settled already.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.12,0:14:13.24,Default,Mechamaru,0,0,0,,{\i1}There's no point in going to Shibuya now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.55,0:14:16.28,Default,Mechamaru,0,0,0,,{\i1}Head back, Miwa.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.65,0:14:33.93,Default,Miwa,0,0,0,,Why only Todo{**-senpai} and Nitta{**-kun}?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.93,0:14:38.41,Default,Mechamaru,0,0,0,,{\i1}I reasoned there's a 99% chance that Todo won't die in Shibuya.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.80,0:14:41.86,Default,Mechamaru,0,0,0,,{\i1}Same for Nitta if he accompanied Todo.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.86,0:14:43.90,Default,Mechamaru,0,0,0,,{\i1}His technique would be useful, too{\fscx180}—{\fscx}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.90,0:14:45.12,Default,Miwa,0,0,0,,And me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.87,0:14:53.67,Default,Miwa,0,0,0,,Am I useless?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.29,0:15:01.69,Default,Mechamaru,0,0,0,,{\i1}The situation isn't even on that scale anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.08,0:15:03.78,Default,Mechamaru,0,0,0,,{\i1}It wasn't just you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.78,0:15:08.15,Default,Mechamaru,0,0,0,,{\i1}It was Mai, Kamo, Nishimiya, and Utahime, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.15,0:15:13.22,Default,Mechamaru,0,0,0,,{\i1}I took steps to make sure you all were on a mission south of Kyoto on the 31st.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.96,0:15:16.14,Default,Miwa,0,0,0,,Why didn't you say anything to us?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.81,0:15:19.48,Default,Miwa,0,0,0,,Why didn't you ask us for help?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.48,0:15:22.03,Default,Miwa,0,0,0,,Aren't we friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.23,0:15:25.72,Default,Miwa,0,0,0,,Is it because...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.16,0:15:27.38,Default,Miwa,0,0,0,,I'm weak?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.38,0:15:30.36,Default,Mechamaru,0,0,0,,{\i1}No. I'm the one who was weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.53,0:15:34.36,Default,Mechamaru,0,0,0,,{\i1}I went about it the wrong way because I was weak,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.36,0:15:38.62,Default,Mechamaru,0,0,0,,{\i1}and I couldn't even see that mistake through because I was weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.47,0:15:47.90,Default,Mechamaru,0,0,0,,{\i1}There was this girl I loved.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.35,0:15:50.90,Default,Mechamaru,0,0,0,,{\i1}And I didn't care what happened to the world
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.90,0:15:53.64,Default,Mechamaru,0,0,0,,{\i1}as long as I could be at her side and protect her.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.97,0:16:01.60,Default,Mechamaru,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even if that girl didn't want me
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.68,0:16:05.03,Default,Mechamaru,0,0,0,,{\i1}to be the one to protect her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.32,0:16:23.16,Default,Mechamaru,0,0,0,,{\i1}Time's up, Miwa.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.16,0:16:23.88,Default,Miwa,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.79,0:16:27.28,Default,Mechamaru,0,0,0,,{\i1}Goodbye. Thank you{\fscx180}—{\fscx}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.28,0:16:29.20,Default,Miwa,0,0,0,,Don't say goodbye!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.36,0:16:31.19,Default,Mechamaru,0,0,0,,{\i1}Miwa.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.25,0:16:32.30,Default,Miwa,0,0,0,,Mechamaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.30,0:16:33.18,Default,Mechamaru,0,0,0,,{\i1}Miwa!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.14,0:16:36.98,Default,Muta,0,0,0,,Please find happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.27,0:16:43.18,Default,Muta,0,0,0,,Whatever shape it takes, as long as you're happy,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.18,0:16:45.43,Default,Muta,0,0,0,,my wish has come true.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.27,0:16:52.69,Default,Miwa,0,0,0,,{\i1}Mechamaru...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.92,0:17:08.46,Default,Mai,0,0,0,,Utahime{*}{*-sensei}, what Mechamaru did...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.46,0:17:09.95,Default,Utahime,0,0,0,,Will go unquestioned.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.95,0:17:11.80,Default,Utahime,0,0,0,,The man is dead, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.21,0:17:15.34,Default,Kamo,0,0,0,,He held us in awfully low regard, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.05,0:17:16.96,Default,Momo,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.96,0:17:19.59,Default,Momo,0,0,0,,And this whole "Todo{**-kun} wouldn't die" crap?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.59,0:17:22.60,Default,Momo,0,0,0,,Is he saying that we {\i1}would{\i0} die, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.45,0:17:27.39,Default,Momo,0,0,0,,I'll murder whoever makes my cute junior cry.
Comment: 0,0:17:28.11,0:17:28.15,Default,chptr,0,0,0,,{Part C}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.65,0:17:45.79,Default,Mahito,0,0,0,,{\i1}He can switch positions with inanimate objects?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.60,0:18:08.73,Default,Yuji,0,0,0,,{\i1}He split apart!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.38,0:18:25.16,Default,Mahito,0,0,0,,Soul Multiplicity!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.16,0:18:26.00,Default,Mahito,0,0,0,,Body Repel!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.68,0:18:48.64,Default,Mahito,0,0,0,,{\i1}Topknot Gorilla's soul is still at full strength,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.64,0:18:51.51,Default,Mahito,0,0,0,,{\i1}but could I kill him with one touch in my current state?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.11,0:18:56.26,Default,Mahito,0,0,0,,{\i1}Itadori's soul is down to about 10% left.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.91,0:19:00.60,Default,Mahito,0,0,0,,{\i1}And my soul is down to 40%.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.28,0:19:04.03,Default,Mahito,0,0,0,,{\i1}Having my double crushed
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.03,0:19:07.69,Default,Mahito,0,0,0,,{\i1}and eating Itadori's rush of Black Flashes shaved away an awful lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.04,0:19:11.84,Default,Mahito,0,0,0,,{\i1}And that's all thanks to that woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.84,0:19:15.64,Default,Mahito,0,0,0,,{\i1}She was a nobody, but she still left her damn mark behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.17,0:19:19.72,Default,Mahito,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll start by eliminating this annoying switcher first!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.92,0:20:49.18,Default,Todo,0,0,0,,Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.52,0:20:59.20,Default,Todo,0,0,0,,{\i1}If you're satisfied with staying on that level,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.20,0:21:02.44,Default,Todo,0,0,0,,{\i1}you and I won't stay best friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.41,0:21:07.56,Default,Todo,0,0,0,,{\i1}This cursed spirit is already landing Black Flash, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.91,0:21:11.28,Default,Todo,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm the one being left behind right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.28,0:21:14.00,Default,Todo,0,0,0,,{\i1}You've grown strong, Brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.00,0:21:16.46,Default,Todo,0,0,0,,{\i1}Are you satisfied with that,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.46,0:21:18.16,Default,Todo,0,0,0,,{\i1}Aoi Todo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.16,0:21:21.40,Default,Todo,0,0,0,,{\i1}Are you planning to leave your brother alone once again,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.40,0:21:23.29,Default,Todo,0,0,0,,{\i1}Aoi Todo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.98,0:21:45.95,Default,Takada,0,0,0,,{\i1}Tan-taka-tan!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.44,0:21:48.36,Default,Todo,0,0,0,,Black Flash!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.20,0:22:00.75,Default,Mahito,0,0,0,,{\i1}It doesn't matter how powerful your attack is,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.75,0:22:02.58,Default,Mahito,0,0,0,,{\i1}or if you throw out a Black Flash.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.58,0:22:07.04,Default,Mahito,0,0,0,,{\i1}Your attacks don't affect my soul, so they're pointless.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.99,0:22:21.00,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{\an8}However, with that, all three of them were now...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.92,0:22:22.72,Default,Todo,0,0,0,,Smooch!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.72,0:22:27.76,Default,Narration,0,0,0,,...drawing out 120% of their latent potential.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.20,0:22:36.04,Default,Mahito,0,0,0,,Soul Multiplicity!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.20,0:22:37.59,Default,Mahito,0,0,0,,Body Repel!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.16,0:22:43.58,Default,Todo,0,0,0,,{\i1}An omnidirectional attack that makes switching pointless!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.58,0:22:46.12,Default,Todo,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's getting into high gear!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.24,0:23:18.12,Default,Mahito,0,0,0,,Let's kick it up a notch, Itadori!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.12,0:23:20.00,Default,Mahito,0,0,0,,This will be the last time
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.00,0:23:23.75,Default,Mahito,0,0,0,,you and I curse each other!
Comment: 0,0:23:24.97,0:23:25.01,Default,chptr,0,0,0,,{Preview}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.51,0:23:28.53,Default,Todo,0,0,0,,{\an8}They say a hero always arrives late,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.53,0:23:31.69,Default,Todo,0,0,0,,{\an8}but everyone understands that those who worked hard
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.69,0:23:34.34,Default,Todo,0,0,0,,{\an8}and held out are heroes, too, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.34,0:23:36.43,Default,Todo,0,0,0,,{\an8}Next time, Metamorphosis.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.43,0:23:39.52,Default,Utahime,0,0,0,,{\an8}Don't forget to grab your delay certificate!
